### Core MATLAB Files ###
*.asv          # MATLAB autosave files
*.m~           # Editor backup files
*.p            # Obfuscated MATLAB code
*.mlapp        # MATLAB App Designer files
*.mlappinstall # Installed app files
*.mltbx        # Toolbox files
*.mlpkginstall # Package installation files
*.mlsettings   # MATLAB settings files
*.prj          # Project files

### Data & Binary Files ###
*.mat          # MAT-files (comment out if you want to version control data)
*.fig          # Figure files
*.slxc         # Simulink cache files
*.slxp         # Simulink protected model files
*.mex*         # MEX files (platform-specific)

### Cache & Temporary Files ###
mlcache/       # MATLAB cache directory
*.autosave     # Autosave files
*.r20*         # Version-specific cache files
simulinktmp/   # Simulink temporary directory
sccprj/        # Source control project files
