### Build & Deployment ###
deploytool/    # Deployment output
packages/      # Package directories
*.ctf          # Compiled component
*.exe          # Windows executable
*.dll          # Windows dynamic library
*.lib          # Static library
*.exp          # Export files
*.obj          # Object files
*.o            # Object files (Unix)
*.a            # Static libraries (Unix)
